Z) THE VALENCE ELECTRONS ARE ONLY LOOSELY HELD AND CAN MOVE TO
NEIGHBORING ATOMS

A proton enters a uniform magnetic field that is oriented

answer: Z) THE POSITION OF THE PROTON IN THE MAGNETIC FIELD

ENERGY OF THE GAS)
